      delectus voluptates aperiam. Commodi modi soluta velit facere explicabo autem ipsam quo asperiores illo officiis.
    </p>
    <div class="inline">
      <img src="../public/assets/coin.svg" alt="My Image" class="scroll-image rotate-image" />
